The '''Geonosian High Audience Chamber''' was located in the [[Petranaki arena]]. It was there where [[Archduke/Legends|Archduke]] [[Poggle the Lesser/Legends|Poggle the Lesser]] found [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]] guilty of espionage, and sentenced them to be executed in the Arena with [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]].

